{
  "chapter": 140,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙回到都骑官署，荆俊报告抓获调戏周良之妻的吕邦（吕雄之子）。项少龙利用此事设下圈套，向小盘献计散布吕邦奸杀妇女的假消息，诱使吕雄闯入都骑官署要人。同时项少龙提出\"仲父\"称号之计，可安吕不韦之心又使其位高势危。小盘召吕不韦等大臣入宫议事，断绝吕雄求助之路。项少龙出宫时被昌文君截住，其妹嬴盈与鹿丹儿两位刁蛮少女缠着要比试。回到官署，吕雄果然率都卫亲兵来闹事，态度嚣张不敬。项少龙借机发作，斥其不施军礼、口出狂言，吕雄拔剑抗拒，十八铁卫以弩箭射倒其十八名手下。吕雄被迫弃剑投降后，项少龙才揭露真相——吕邦仅是打伤人而已。吕雄方知落入精心设计的陷阱。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "三哥！昨夜钓到一条大鱼！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "什么大鱼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你听过吕邦这人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "是否吕不韦的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不但是吕家贼子之一，还是吕雄的宝贝儿子，这家伙不知如何，看上人家美丽的娇妻，竟当街调戏，刚好徐先路过才解了围。哪知这小子心有不甘，人家小夫妻已离城避开他，色鬼仍锲而不舍，漏夜率领十多名家将追出城去，截着人家，打伤了男的，正要对女的行淫时，给我及时赶到，将他和一众从犯当场逮捕。哈！你说这条鱼够大吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "你怎能去得那样及时？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "全赖陶公的情报组，知道此事后立即通知小弟。我最清楚吕邦的性格，他看上的东西从不肯罢休。于是乎着人监视他，这小子果然给逮个正着。今趟确是万分精彩，秦人对奸淫之徒，刑法严峻，只要将吕邦解送都律所，他怎样都逃不了刑罚，最好给他来个阉刑，只要想想吕雄心痛的样子，可为倩公主她们稍出一口恶气。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "现在吕邦等人被扣押在哪里，相国府的人知道这件事吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨夜我把有关人等，包括那对年轻夫妇，全部秘密送到这里来，吕邦和他的人给关在牢里。唉！不过却有个头痛的问题，这小子当然矢口不认，推得一干二净，最糟糕是那对受害的小夫妻知道吕邦是相国府的人后，慌了起来，不肯挺身作证，只是求我放他们走，说以后再不想踏足咸阳城了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "二哥呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他今早的心情看来不佳，问吕邦没够两句就赏他一个耳光，现在去向那小夫妻软硬兼施，真怕他会忍不住揍人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "先去看二哥再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_liang",
      "speaker_name": "周良",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "恩公！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你们认识项大人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhou_liang",
      "text": "这事迟点再说！贤夫妇差点为奸人所害，何故却不肯指证他们？岂非任由恶人逍遥法外，说不定很快又有别的人遭他们的毒手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_liang",
      "speaker_name": "周良",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只要是恩公吩咐，愚夫妇纵使为此事送命，亦不会有半点犹豫。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_zhou_liang",
      "text": "两位放心，事后我们会派人送两位离去，保证没有人可以伤害你们。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhou_liang",
      "text": "最迟明天早上，贤伉俪应可远离险境。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "犯事的只是吕邦，况且他又没有真的奸淫那妇女，只可将他重重打几杖，很难真的拿他怎样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "微臣看项统领胸内早有奇谋妙计！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "想瞒过李大人确是难比登天，我现正安排把消息巧妙地传入他爹吕雄的耳内，骗吕雄说他的宝贝儿子犯了奸杀良家妇女的头等大罪，只要他情急下闯进都骑官署来要人，我或有方法教他入彀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "吕雄究竟是怎样的一个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "此人是个急功近利、好大喜功的庸材，自到秦国后，便以吕不韦之下吕族中的第二号人物自居，气焰逼人，据闻今趟他虽当上都卫副统领，却是非常不服气给管中邪骑在头上，见到管中邪也不肯致敬施礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项卿竟对相府的事如此清楚？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "吕不韦可以收买我的人，臣下自不会对他客气。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "吕雄若是这么一个人，确是可以利用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_li_si",
      "text": "李卿家立即使人把吕不韦、鹿公、徐先、王龁、蒙骜、蔡泽、王绾等人召入宫来议事，寡人务要令吕雄求助无门，好教他鲁莽行事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此事闹得愈大愈好，我可藉此事立威，一杀吕不韦的气焰，这奸贼最近得到太后的支持，更是趾高气扬，竟向太后进言要正式把他册封为摄政大臣，确是无耻之尤。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "太后怎么说呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太后给嫪毐迷得神魂颠倒，除在师父的事上不肯让步外，对他总是言听计从，曾两次找我去说话，唉！为了这事，我两晚睡不安寝。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "那不如给他打个折扣，只封他为仲父，顺便害害他。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "此事必须在滴血认亲后方可进行，否则会招来反效果。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我岂非真的认贼作父吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "这不外是个虚衔，全无实质的权力，却有两个好处。首先是安奸贼的心，教他再难以提出更狂妄的要求；另一方面却可使鹿公等对他更是不满，由于有滴血认亲的如山铁证，鹿公等大臣只会认为是吕不韦硬把自己捧作'假王父'，使他更是位高势危，没有好日子过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "师父为何竟能随意想出这么特别的名衔？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "我也不知道，只是脑海里忽然冒出这个名词。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此事待我想想，师父啊！我并非不采纳你的意见，只因事关重大，还该听听李斯的想法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "储君开始有自己的灼见，我高兴还来不及，怎会不高兴？看着你长大成人，已是我最大的欣慰。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "吕雄应接到消息了，我该回去应付他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "师父可否见见母后，只有你可使母后脱离嫪毐的控制。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "看看怎办吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙先原谅我泄露你行踪的过错，舍妹正在宫门处候你，嘿！你该知她不会有什么好事做出来的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "text": "那我只好由别处溜走。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "万勿如此，那样她就知是我泄露她的事，你还是去敷衍敷衍她吧！当是卖个人情给我，今晚我来找你去喝酒，以作赔罪。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "text": "我听过有对子女二十四孝的老爹，似你般对妹子二十四孝的亲兄，就从所未闻也。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我看舍妹对少龙很有好感，当然哩！她嘴上怎也不肯承认，但只要看到她昨晚见过你后兴奋雀跃的样子，便瞒不过她哥哥我一对锐利的眼睛。哈！她算不错吧！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "text": "莫要说笑，先让我去看她又有什么耍弄我的手段。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项将军你好，我们姊妹不服气，又来找你较量了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "哪有这么无赖的，项少龙你是否男子汉大丈夫？我不管你，快随我们到城外去先比骑术，再比其他的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹿丹儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是否又多个胆怯没用的家伙哩！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "算我怕你们，比什么都可以，但我要先返官署处理一些事后，才陪你们玩耍。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁要和你玩耍？只是见你还勉强像点样儿，本姑娘才有兴趣秤秤你的斤两。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹿丹儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "男人都是这样，给点颜色当作大红，嘿！臭美的！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "不让我回去官署便拉倒，你们不稀罕就算了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "稀罕？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管你们要怎样也好！弟兄们，我们回署去了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "都骑军",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "统领，都卫的人来闹事。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "都卫不是你辖下的人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "你两个乖乖留在这里，不要让他们知道，好给我做个见证。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "可以说话的人终于回来了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "吕大人口中那个'可以说话的人'，未知指的是何人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "指的当然是项统领，你不是可以话事的人吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "好大胆！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "吕雄你见到本将军，不施军礼，已是不敬，还口出狂言，没有上下尊卑，是否知罪？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "统领若认为我吕雄犯错，大可向吕相投诉。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "异日吕雄你若被派往沙场，是否亦只听吕相一人的话，只有他才能管你呢？或事事派人回咸阳找吕相评理？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "荆俊你算什么东西，竟敢……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "他若不算东西，你更不算东西，大家是副统领，说起来荆副统领还比你要高上半级。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "吕雄你太放肆，给我跪下！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙你莫要逼人太甚！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人来，给项统领把违令狂徒拿下！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢动手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "吕副统领若不立刻放下手中兵器，跪地受缚，休怪我手下不留情。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你能拿我怎样？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "你手上的长剑是什么意思，我们手上的弩箭就是那种意思，你说是什么意思？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两个女娃儿是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "都骑军校尉",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "竟连这两位鼎鼎有名的女英雄嬴盈小姐和鹿丹儿小姐都不识芳驾，吕雄你当什么都卫副统领。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "吕雄你若不立即弃剑下跪，我会教你后悔莫及！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "射脚！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "算你狠！我倒要看你怎样向吕相交代。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "吕副统领，这是何苦来由？令郎只不过是打伤个人，为何要闹得动刀动枪的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiong",
      "text": "你听不清楚吗？不过什么都没有关系。现在我就和你到吕相处评评理，看看是谁不分尊卑？是谁以下犯上？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 140,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 414
    }
